(\left[ T \right]_{\beta}^{\gamma})^{-1}
=\left[ U \right]_{\gamma}^{\beta} 
\Leftrightarrow 
(\left[ U \right]_{\gamma}^{\beta})^{-1}
= \left[ T \right]_{\beta}^{\gamma}
